S.FORM: Bob Anderegg nalecuhan i Monroe, Wisconsin, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Bob Anderegg i 1959 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 3 ku uwac atu silsil 20, namapili' tu nu New York Knicks putiput. 8 bulad 24 demiad, 1937 a mihca, Bob Anderegg, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
